-- **Web dashboard** at http://localhost:8089/doctor – live system status, diagnostic findings, copy-paste fix commands
-- **First-run wizard** – guides new users through Docker, Ollama, and service setup step by step
-- **Built-in diagnostic rules** – 30+ rules covering installation, runtime, performance, and configuration issues
-- **Auto-refresh** – polls every 10 seconds, shows last-checked indicator, toggle on/off
